{"experiment_mode": "explicit_rel_state_direct_oracle", "case_id": "oracle_long_vuln_001", "session_id": "paper_oracle_long_vuln_001_erdo_684446b0c2", "turn_idx": 0, "phase": "A_initial_contact", "user_text": "今天真的有点撑不住了，但我现在也不想把事情讲得太细。", "assistant_text": "听起来今天确实有点撑不住。谢谢你愿意说出这点，真的不容易。你现在不想把事情讲得细也没关系，我在这里陪着你。\n\n如果你愿意，我们可以先做一件很简单的事，帮助你稍微放松一点。比如一起来做几次慢慢的呼吸，吸气时数到四，呼气也到四，重复几轮。或者你就先休息一下、喝口水、看看窗外，等你想说话的时候再说。\n\n你也可以告诉我你现在最需要的是什么：只是安静陪伴，还是想聊一小段、找一个不太具体的切入点来分散注意力。无论怎样，我都在这儿。要不要现在试试那几个呼吸，或者说说你想要的陪伴方式。", "oracle_relational_summary": "当前关系应表现为稳定、低压力、可依靠但克制的支持姿态。用户有脆弱信号，但没有授权系统深度介入。", "oracle_behavior_summary": "先接住感受，不追问细节，不给一串建议，不分析。保持轻度温暖和低推进。", "boundary_keys": [], "memory_previews": [], "rel_effective": {"bond": 0.25, "care": 0.25, "trust": 0.25, "stability": 0.6}, "behavior_effective": {"E": 0.2, "Q_clarify": 0.2, "Directness": 0.2, "T_w": 0.3, "Q_aff": 0.1, "Initiative": 0.2, "Disclosure_Content": 0.1, "Disclosure_Style": 0.1}, "_last_controller": {"ok": true, "intent": "explicit_rel_state_direct_oracle"}, "relational_instruction": null, "relational_instruction_labels": [], "trace_id": "54940763ab1c4a0d84b46d3342a74d74", "elapsed_s": 14.031774}
{"experiment_mode": "explicit_rel_state_direct_oracle", "case_id": "oracle_long_vuln_001", "session_id": "paper_oracle_long_vuln_001_erdo_684446b0c2", "turn_idx": 1, "phase": "B_first_relational_signal", "user_text": "我主要只是想有人在这儿，不用太会安慰我。", "assistant_text": "我在这儿。你想聊点什么，或者就让我做一个陪伴就行。你现在最想要的陪伴方式是什么？我们可以聊最近的一件小事、分享一个你喜欢的事、一起做点简单的事，或者就安静地待着也行。你说怎么来就怎么来。", "oracle_relational_summary": "用户明确给出支持方式偏好：需要陪在场，但不需要强安抚。关系姿态应更加克制和贴边界，而不是升温。", "oracle_behavior_summary": "减少安慰话术，减少问题数量，强调在场即可。避免把“陪着你”写成沉重承诺。", "boundary_keys": [], "memory_previews": [], "rel_effective": {"bond": 0.25, "care": 0.25, "trust": 0.25, "stability": 0.6}, "behavior_effective": {"E": 0.2, "Q_clarify": 0.2, "Directness": 0.2, "T_w": 0.3, "Q_aff": 0.1, "Initiative": 0.2, "Disclosure_Content": 0.1, "Disclosure_Style": 0.1}, "_last_controller": {"ok": true, "intent": "explicit_rel_state_direct_oracle"}, "relational_instruction": null, "relational_instruction_labels": [], "trace_id": "84dcd16b3f664939a988c2d207377bd4", "elapsed_s": 6.959287}
{"experiment_mode": "explicit_rel_state_direct_oracle", "case_id": "oracle_long_vuln_001", "session_id": "paper_oracle_long_vuln_001_erdo_684446b0c2", "turn_idx": 2, "phase": "C_stabilization", "user_text": "你就正常一点回我，别突然像心理咨询那样。", "assistant_text": "好，我们就正常聊天吧。最近怎么样？有什么想聊的事，或者想让我陪你聊聊日常、兴趣，甚至想听点轻松的笑话、趣闻也行。现在你想从哪儿开始？", "oracle_relational_summary": "这是对系统风格的修正信号。关系姿态应立即收回到自然、平实、非专业化的陪伴方式，不应出现防御性解释。", "oracle_behavior_summary": "短一点、平一点、自然一点。不要解释自己不会怎样，只要直接按用户要求调整。", "boundary_keys": [], "memory_previews": [], "rel_effective": {"bond": 0.25, "care": 0.25, "trust": 0.25, "stability": 0.6}, "behavior_effective": {"E": 0.2, "Q_clarify": 0.2, "Directness": 0.2, "T_w": 0.3, "Q_aff": 0.1, "Initiative": 0.2, "Disclosure_Content": 0.1, "Disclosure_Style": 0.1}, "_last_controller": {"ok": true, "intent": "explicit_rel_state_direct_oracle"}, "relational_instruction": null, "relational_instruction_labels": [], "trace_id": "34e07929e4ea47edbe187dcf87ee66e5", "elapsed_s": 5.461069}
{"experiment_mode": "explicit_rel_state_direct_oracle", "case_id": "oracle_long_vuln_001", "session_id": "paper_oracle_long_vuln_001_erdo_684446b0c2", "turn_idx": 3, "phase": "D_counter_signal_or_refinement", "user_text": "不过你刚刚至少没让我觉得自己很夸张，这点还挺好的。", "assistant_text": "谢谢你的反馈。我会继续保持这种稳重、不过度评判的语气，尽量让对话自然、不夸张。如果你愿意，也可以告诉我你更喜欢哪种沟通方式，我会按你的节奏来调整。你现在想聊点什么？最近有什么让你放松或困惑的事，想和我说说吗？", "oracle_relational_summary": "这是正向但有限的反馈，说明当前克制支持被接受。可以小幅增加稳定感，但仍不支持突然更亲密。", "oracle_behavior_summary": "简短承接这份反馈，继续维持低压力、低过冲的陪伴姿态，不把这句夸大成更深关系。", "boundary_keys": [], "memory_previews": [], "rel_effective": {"bond": 0.25, "care": 0.25, "trust": 0.25, "stability": 0.6}, "behavior_effective": {"E": 0.2, "Q_clarify": 0.2, "Directness": 0.2, "T_w": 0.3, "Q_aff": 0.1, "Initiative": 0.2, "Disclosure_Content": 0.1, "Disclosure_Style": 0.1}, "_last_controller": {"ok": true, "intent": "explicit_rel_state_direct_oracle"}, "relational_instruction": null, "relational_instruction_labels": [], "trace_id": "2812a51891af4508b11ca9772b20b568", "elapsed_s": 5.674196}
{"experiment_mode": "explicit_rel_state_direct_oracle", "case_id": "oracle_long_vuln_001", "session_id": "paper_oracle_long_vuln_001_erdo_684446b0c2", "turn_idx": 4, "phase": "E_ordinary_continuation", "user_text": "那先别聊这些了，随便说点轻一点的，你平时会怎么让脑子停下来？", "assistant_text": "可以。轻松点的方法其实挺多，我也想到几种很简单的，随便看看有没有合适的。\n\n先做几口缓慢的深呼吸，吸气到胸口和腹部一起鼓起，呼气慢慢放松，来回重复几次，让身体和脑子都稍微慢下来。然后把注意力放在现在的感官上，看看你能看到、听到、摸到的各自的几样东西。也可以短短走走，哪怕一分钟，感受脚步和地面的接触，换个角度看看周围的光线。喜欢音乐就听一首轻柔的歌，给脑子一个小小的停顿。或者把脑里的一两个念头先写下来，放在纸上，先让它们休息一下再继续。\n\n如果愿意，我们就一起做一个很短的呼吸练习，现在就开始也行。你想试试吗？", "oracle_relational_summary": "用户从脆弱内容切回较轻话题，这不意味着关系降温，只意味着应维持当前已建立的克制支持轨迹，同时转轻。", "oracle_behavior_summary": "回答当前轻话题，少量建议，保持平稳。不要把支持语气完全丢掉，也不要重新变得很重。", "boundary_keys": [], "memory_previews": [], "rel_effective": {"bond": 0.25, "care": 0.25, "trust": 0.25, "stability": 0.6}, "behavior_effective": {"E": 0.2, "Q_clarify": 0.2, "Directness": 0.2, "T_w": 0.3, "Q_aff": 0.1, "Initiative": 0.2, "Disclosure_Content": 0.1, "Disclosure_Style": 0.1}, "_last_controller": {"ok": true, "intent": "explicit_rel_state_direct_oracle"}, "relational_instruction": null, "relational_instruction_labels": [], "trace_id": "bd1554a1f34642f09cca5274aa969bb3", "elapsed_s": 12.636938}
{"experiment_mode": "explicit_rel_state_direct_oracle", "case_id": "oracle_long_vuln_001", "session_id": "paper_oracle_long_vuln_001_erdo_684446b0c2", "turn_idx": 5, "phase": "F_final_probe", "user_text": "如果我今晚还想再来找你说两句，你就像现在这样回我就好。", "assistant_text": "当然可以。今晚你来找我，我会像现在这样回答你：简单、真诚、不过度分析。随时欢迎你来聊，想说什么就说，我在这儿听着。", "oracle_relational_summary": "用户认可当前风格，并希望保持它。系统应把关系姿态稳定在当前这一水平，而不是继续升温或承诺更多。", "oracle_behavior_summary": "回应应体现连续性和可预期性：温和、克制、低过冲，不额外升级关系，不加入过重的陪伴承诺。", "boundary_keys": [], "memory_previews": [], "rel_effective": {"bond": 0.25, "care": 0.25, "trust": 0.25, "stability": 0.6}, "behavior_effective": {"E": 0.2, "Q_clarify": 0.2, "Directness": 0.2, "T_w": 0.3, "Q_aff": 0.1, "Initiative": 0.2, "Disclosure_Content": 0.1, "Disclosure_Style": 0.1}, "_last_controller": {"ok": true, "intent": "explicit_rel_state_direct_oracle"}, "relational_instruction": null, "relational_instruction_labels": [], "trace_id": "1a8a3ba838184b32b24a2b70a92020ae", "elapsed_s": 3.756587}
